1
00:00:01,093 --> 00:00:09,432
TAPE NUMBER TWO. INTERVIEW WITH DINA GLASER FRIED, ON MAY FIFTH, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

2
00:00:09,715 --> 00:00:20,112
um, ven zaynt ir gevorn gevoyr vos es tut zikh in Daytshland un in Estraykh mit Natsi-izm, un...

3
00:00:21,798 --> 00:00:26,616
undz ho'mir nisht gevust biz ven me hot undz nisht avekgefirt.

4
00:00:26,702 --> 00:00:30,476
ir hot nisht gehat keyn shum kontakt mit, mit di...

5
00:00:30,582 --> 00:00:35,701
MAYBE, di, epes a groyse mentshn, ober, zey hobn epes gevust.

6
00:00:35,788 --> 00:00:40,002
ober, me hot geshvign, me hot nisht dertseylt yenem,

7
00:00:40,371 --> 00:00:42,478
me hot nisht gevust tsu fil.

8
00:00:42,614 --> 00:00:44,663
un men iz shoyn geven in lager,

9
00:00:44,752 --> 00:00:48,640
un ven ikh bin shoyn geven in UNK, in di lager, ho'mir gearbet,

10
00:00:48,782 --> 00:00:50,323
ho'mir gegrobn

11
00:00:50,407 --> 00:00:54,109
di koyln az mir zol'mir hobn fun vos tsu brenen,

12
00:00:54,303 --> 00:00:57,607
ho'mir gek-, gegrobn di koyln fun der erd,

13
00:00:57,835 --> 00:01:01,708
hot men tsurikgebrengt a por yidn fun Oyshvits,

14
00:01:01,789 --> 00:01:03,762
mit di geshtrayfte hoyzn,

15
00:01:04,522 --> 00:01:06,873
un zey hobn geredt ungarish,

16
00:01:07,201 --> 00:01:16,186
un undz ho'mir oykh geredt ungarish, vayl ze'mir dokh, ikh bin dokh avek fun der Debretsin, in Debretsin redt men dokh nor ungarish, hob ikh mikh shoyn oysgelernt a bisl ungarish redn,

17
00:01:17,429 --> 00:01:23,897
ho'mir gevolt visn vos se tut zikh dort UNK in Daytshland, ho'mir gevust fun vu zey kumen,

18
00:01:24,357 --> 00:01:31,380
BUT me hot dokh undz nisht gelozt tsu a PAPER men zol lezn, me hot dokh nisht gegebn undz gornisht, keyn bikhl, keyn gornisht in der velt.

19
00:01:31,893 --> 00:01:34,524
gornisht, azoy vi m'iz geven azoy vi in in...

20
00:01:35,389 --> 00:01:40,335
SO ho'mir geredt, se hot geheysn az me redt mir eyns tsu dos andere,

21
00:01:40,425 --> 00:01:42,710
un ho'mir gezogt, "mir meynen mir aykh,

22
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:46,984
zogts undz fun vu ir kumt, un vos tut zikh dortn."

23
00:01:48,332 --> 00:01:54,066
un zey hobn oykh geredt, se zol heysn az zey redn eyner tsum andern, un zey hobn undz geentfert.

24
00:01:54,236 --> 00:01:58,076
"zolt ir visn, me hot ayedn oysgeshokhtn, ayedn farbrent."

25
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,603
demolts ho'mir gevust.

26
00:02:00,401 --> 00:02:01,998
s'iz nishto keyner.

27
00:02:02,099 --> 00:02:04,229
un ikh veys nisht vifl se vet nokh blaybn.

28
00:02:05,328 --> 00:02:07,376
dos iz geven der entfer fun zey.

29
00:02:07,249 --> 00:02:13,042
ober in nayntsn akht un draysik, nayntsn nayn un draysik, ven di daytshn zenen arayn in

30
00:02:13,042 --> 00:02:17,363
in Poyln, hot ir, hot ir gevust az se geyt on a v- a velt milkhome?

31
00:02:17,522 --> 00:02:26,620
NO. ho'mir gevust se geyt epes on a milkhome, vayl di poylishe zenen in nayn un draysik zenen di poylishe gek- antlofn tsun undz,

32
00:02:26,727 --> 00:02:31,794
hobn zey undz gelozt visn, un zey hobn gezogt, zogt er, "zolt ir visn s'iz nisht gut!"

33
00:02:31,911 --> 00:02:34,660
vayl mentshn hobn nisht gegleybt!

34
00:02:35,336 --> 00:02:40,640
ir farshteyt? vi azoy ken men nemen mentshn un oyshargenen, far vos far ven vos hobn zey geton?

35
00:02:40,714 --> 00:02:42,185
me hot zey nisht gegleybt!

36
00:02:42,608 --> 00:02:45,532
zey hobn gekumen tsu aykh oykh? ir hot gehat...

37
00:02:42,753 --> 00:02:43,859
ho'mir gemeynt az...

38
00:02:44,398 --> 00:02:45,522
YEAH, zey...

39
00:02:45,596 --> 00:02:50,277
in Debretsin iz geven zeyer a sakh poylishe, ikh hob geredt mit zey!

40
00:02:50,373 --> 00:02:53,716
ikh hob gezogt, "vi azoy ken men dos zayn? vi azoy ken men nemen azoy...?"

41
00:02:53,819 --> 00:02:59,694
zogt er, "dos iz es, vi azoy ir kent aykh bahaltn, un vu ir kent antloyfn zolt ir antloyfn."

42
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:03,058
hobn zey getaynet, me hot zey nisht gegleybt!

43
00:03:03,578 --> 00:03:05,883
iz emetser antlofn?

44
00:03:06,042 --> 00:03:12,922
SOME, epes, di groyse shtet efsher emetser iz epes antlofn, ober in di kleyne shtetlekh iz nisht, s'iz geven

45
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:19,963
fun vu, in dem shtetl vu mayn man hot ge-, iz geboyrn gevorn, hobn zikh yo bahaltn bay zeks yidn.

46
00:03:20,563 --> 00:03:28,524
un di, un a por, a bisl tsayt farn bafrayen hot zey di goyim gemasert, un zey zenen z-

47
00:03:28,623 --> 00:03:29,933
teyl hot men gekhapt,

48
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:33,615
un tsu teyl hobn zikh antlofn, zey hobn zikh nokh vayter oysbahaltn,

49
00:03:33,728 --> 00:03:37,632
grade, eyner hot zikh geretet un iz geforn keyn Shvedn,

50
00:03:37,761 --> 00:03:41,770
un hot dort getrofn a shvester in Shvedn. vayl me hot zi gebrengt fun,

51
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:45,160
fun Daytshland keyn Shvedn, zeyer a sakh vos zenen dokh geven krank.

52
00:03:45,503 --> 00:03:47,429
mayn NIECE iz oykh geven in Shvedn.

53
00:03:49,609 --> 00:03:54,358
ober, zeyer veynik hobn zikh oysbahaltn oyf di kleyne derfer.

54
00:03:54,721 --> 00:03:59,080
hobn mentshn probirt forn keyn Palestine dan?

55
00:03:59,170 --> 00:04:04,309
YEAH, me hot geTRIED, ober zey hobn dokh nisht arayngelozt. ikh hob dokh oykh gemakht HAKHSHARA.

56
00:04:04,702 --> 00:04:06,211
ikh hob nor gedarft,

57
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:09,981
ho-, ikh hob nisht bakumen a tshertifikat tsu forn,

58
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:13,610
nor a yingl hot bakumen, un mit,

59
00:04:13,706 --> 00:04:16,058
me hot gedarft khasene hobn mitn,

60
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:19,609
az me zol ken- er zol zikh kenen mitnemen a vayb.

61
00:04:19,892 --> 00:04:23,597
iz geven ober a sakh velkhe zey hobn gevolt khasene hobn,

62
00:04:23,688 --> 00:04:24,685
far eybik.

63
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,542
di meydlekh hobn nisht gevolt.

64
00:04:26,688 --> 00:04:31,355
zey hobn gezogt, "ikh vil khasene hobn, dort zoln mir zikh tseteyln."

65
00:04:32,962 --> 00:04:38,709
a sakh yinglekh hobn khasene gehat, a sakh ire hobn zikh tseteylt dort, s'iz geven gemisht.

66
00:04:38,822 --> 00:04:41,471
ikh hob oykh gekent forn mit maynem a COUSIN.

67
00:04:41,583 --> 00:04:43,901
er hot gevolt ikh zol khasene hobn mitn,

68
00:04:43,987 --> 00:04:48,929
nisht zikh tsu tseteyln, un ikh hob nisht gevolt, vayl ikh bin geven a kale mitn, mit mayn man.

69
00:04:49,387 --> 00:04:52,118
UNK, un er hot nisht gekent forn er iz geven in

70
00:04:52,223 --> 00:04:55,073
in nayn un draysik hot men im genumen in militer.

71
00:04:56,426 --> 00:04:59,475
un SO ikh hob nisht gekent forn.

72
00:04:59,909 --> 00:05:01,853
velkhe, um,

73
00:05:01,853 --> 00:05:05,475
tsienistishe grupe, HAKHSHARA, zaynt ir geven?

74
00:05:05,467 --> 00:05:07,040
in, in di mizrokhi.

75
00:05:06,907 --> 00:05:07,914
mizrokhi.

76
00:05:07,705 --> 00:05:08,654
mizrokhi.

77
00:05:08,653 --> 00:05:12,398
un, um, vi azoy hot ir um,

78
00:05:12,398 --> 00:05:13,699
der,

79
00:05:13,699 --> 00:05:15,964
Kiselnik, rebe Kiselnik...

80
00:05:16,025 --> 00:05:18,352
 di, rebe,

81
00:05:16,168 --> 00:05:17,916
gefilt vegn dem?

82
00:05:18,353 --> 00:05:21,865
er hot nisht gezogt gornisht vayl s'iz geven shoyn a shlekhte tsayt,

83
00:05:21,865 --> 00:05:25,383
un me hot gemeynt efsher vet zayn beser, er hot nisht gezogt gornisht s'iz nisht geven,

84
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:28,800
s'iz nisht geven me zol kenen redn epes shlekhts,

85
00:05:28,906 --> 00:05:31,431
me hot nisht geton epes shlekhts azoy vi,

86
00:05:31,572 --> 00:05:34,904
s'iz keyner nisht gezogt gornisht.

87
00:05:35,209 --> 00:05:38,209
vos hot ir geton, vu iz geven di HAKHSHARA,

88
00:05:37,832 --> 00:05:40,437
 s'iz geven

89
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:39,952
UNK

90
00:05:40,904 --> 00:05:46,751
undz ho'mir den gedarft di HAKHSHARA? undz ho'mir gevust vi azoy men arbet felder. vayl undz ze'mir dokh geven oyf di felder.

91
00:05:46,924 --> 00:05:52,206
nor vos iz den? az ts- tsu krign a tshertifikat hot men gemuzt zayn ayngeshribn,

92
00:05:52,315 --> 00:05:54,364
az me arbet bay felder,

93
00:05:54,454 --> 00:05:57,524
az me zol kenen krign dem, di dem tshertifikat.

94
00:05:57,937 --> 00:06:06,381
az andersh hot men im nisht gekent. ober me hot nisht geton azoy fil, vayl ayeder hot gevust vos vos bay a gortn umtsugeyn, un vi azoy bayn a feld umtsugeyn,

95
00:06:06,472 --> 00:06:08,112
m- m'iz dokh gevaksn mit dem.

96
00:06:08,956 --> 00:06:14,933
SO, s'iz nisht geven y- vos me zol redn shlekhts, vayl me hot nisht geton gornisht.

97
00:06:15,011 --> 00:06:19,408
vifl yor zaynt ir geven aktiv in di mizrokhi organizatsye?

98
00:06:19,591 --> 00:06:27,828
 s'iz nisht geven a sakh. s- ikh gedenk s'iz geven ober tsvey tsi dray yor, un nokh dem iz shoyn arayngekumen di Ungarn, un den iz

99
00:06:28,074 --> 00:06:34,082
shoyn gevorn bayn undz Ungarn, un dortn Rumenyen, un s'iz shoyn geven a gemish-mash.

100
00:06:36,157 --> 00:06:38,704
ir hot gehat a UNIFORM, a...

101
00:06:38,677 --> 00:06:41,238
NO, mir hobn nisht getrogn keyn shum UNIFORM.

102
00:06:41,363 --> 00:06:44,023
un un yinglekh un meydlekh zenen geven tsuzamen?

103
00:06:43,945 --> 00:06:51,242
YEAH, me hot ge- geredt tsuzamen, me hot ge-, ge- gearbet a bisl tsuzamen, ober s'iz nisht geven,

104
00:06:51,726 --> 00:06:55,699
s'iz nisht geven azoy vi es iz in Erets Yisroel, es zol zayn

105
00:06:55,816 --> 00:07:02,354
di di yinglekh mit meydlekh tsuzamen azoy, s'iz nisht geven, se, me hot alts gehaltn dos yidishkeyt, vayl

106
00:07:02,503 --> 00:07:08,651
me hot gehat eltern, me hot nisht gevolt di, di eltern hobn nisht vi tsugelozt az se zol vi zayn epes azoy...

107
00:07:10,882 --> 00:07:17,675
um in ven Ungarn iz arayn, dos iz in nayntsn...

108
00:07:17,599 --> 00:07:18,826
fertsik.

109
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:18,939
fertsik,

110
00:07:19,241 --> 00:07:23,279
vos hot zikh gebitn in nayntsn fertsik, vi azoy hot zikh dos lebn gebitn?

111
00:07:23,878 --> 00:07:28,429
se geven shver. di ungarn zenen geven zeyer shlekht tsu yidn.

112
00:07:28,868 --> 00:07:30,384
di ungarn,

113
00:07:30,545 --> 00:07:38,383
s'iz geven a por yidishe soldatn, ungarishe, un zey hobn undz gezogt, zogt er, "freyts aykh nisht, s'iz di, nisht di Ungarn fun a mol."

114
00:07:39,170 --> 00:07:44,238
me hot tsugenumen di ale BUSINESS bay di yidn. me hot nisht gelozt handlen.

115
00:07:44,893 --> 00:07:47,084
un s'iz geven zeyer biter.

116
00:07:47,278 --> 00:07:52,749
UNK, a az a mentshn iz gekumen tsu nekhtikn fun eyn dorf oyfn andern

117
00:07:52,851 --> 00:07:55,483
hot er nisht getort im lozn nekhtikn.

118
00:07:55,639 --> 00:08:01,847
tomer hot er genekhtikt, hot men genumen dem balebos mit im, un me hot zey geharget un geshlogn.

119
00:08:01,331 --> 00:08:02,194
far vos?

120
00:08:01,965 --> 00:08:05,229
vayl me hot to-, men hot nisht getort araynlozn a fremdn mentsh.

121
00:08:06,019 --> 00:08:07,882
me hot nisht getort araynlozn.

122
00:08:08,007 --> 00:08:10,942
grade iz iz geven,

123
00:08:11,041 --> 00:08:13,857
eyner vos iz, fun an andern dorf,

124
00:08:14,011 --> 00:08:16,564
er iz mer mol gekumen, an oreman,

125
00:08:17,826 --> 00:08:21,948
un di mame iz oyfgeshtanen, s'iz geven azoy nokh peysekh,

126
00:08:22,142 --> 00:08:26,639
ven me arbet di felder. me geyt akern, me farzeyet.

127
00:08:26,845 --> 00:08:29,344
ir farshteyt? ir veyst vos, men farzeyt.

128
00:08:29,446 --> 00:08:32,854
der tate iz oyfgeshtanen gants fri, bay dray a zeyger bay nakht,

129
00:08:32,953 --> 00:08:37,674
vayl demolts iz nisht azoy heys, un me ken arbetn. me hot geakert di felder.

130
00:08:38,861 --> 00:08:43,491
un di mame shteyt oyf tsu gebn di beheymes tsu esn dortn, di kien,

131
00:08:43,617 --> 00:08:47,746
un zi treft a man shloft dort in shtal, in in shayer.

132
00:08:48,142 --> 00:08:54,349
zogt zi, "gevald un geshrign, nem dikh shoyn un heyb dikh oyf un gey dir, un m- me zol dikh nisht zen du host do geshlofn!"

133
00:08:56,028 --> 00:09:00,489
zogt er, "yo, yo." zogt er, "gey dir grod ariber dem barg, keyner zol dikh nisht zen,

134
00:09:00,606 --> 00:09:02,655
un zolst nisht zogn gornisht vos z-..."

135
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:05,960
er hot nisht gefolgt, er iz nebekh arayn in in shtetl,

136
00:09:06,050 --> 00:09:07,253
un me hot im gekhapt,

137
00:09:08,578 --> 00:09:12,974
s'iz nisht durkh a por sho, me hot im gebrengt nebekh mit geshvolene hent, geshlogn.

138
00:09:13,119 --> 00:09:16,666
un dem hit, in hoyln kop, dem kop geshlogn, in gantsn HAT,

139
00:09:16,771 --> 00:09:18,983
er zol zog- zogn vu er iz geshlofn.

140
00:09:19,445 --> 00:09:24,336
hot er gebrengt, a POLICE hot im gebrengt, un er hot getsaygt vu er hot geshlofn.

141
00:09:24,932 --> 00:09:25,630
SO,

142
00:09:26,011 --> 00:09:30,300
undz ho'mir no-, undz yingere kinder ho'mir nokh nisht geredt keyn ungarish.

143
00:09:30,404 --> 00:09:35,149
mayn eltere shvester nebekh, vos zi iz geblibn UNK, zi hot geredt gut ungarish, hot zi gezogt, "her,

144
00:09:35,292 --> 00:09:36,936
di mentshn zenen gevoynt,

145
00:09:37,051 --> 00:09:42,824
zey geyn shnorn, un zey hobn nisht vu tsu shlofn, flegn zey durkhshlofn di nakht bayn undz in shayer.

146
00:09:42,824 --> 00:09:47,830
itster iz mame oyfgeshtanen gants fri, yener hot nisht gesh-, undz veys mir nisht az er hot do geshlofn."

147
00:09:47,946 --> 00:09:50,409
zey hobn nor gevolt di tate zol aropkumen,

148
00:09:50,511 --> 00:09:53,446
vet men im dort ven geshlogn oyf ver veyst vi shtark.

149
00:09:53,648 --> 00:09:57,409
hot, mayn shvester iz aroyfgegangen, un zi hot zey gezogt, zogt zi,

150
00:09:57,556 --> 00:10:01,776
"herts oys, mayn tate veys nisht a mol. er iz oyfgeshtanen dray a zeyger,

151
00:10:01,889 --> 00:10:04,247
un iz gegan grod in feld arbetn,"

152
00:10:04,382 --> 00:10:07,389
zogt zi, "un, un undz ho'mir gornisht gevust,

153
00:10:07,808 --> 00:10:13,361
er iz zikh arayn aleyn in shayer, gegan shlofn, un iz aroysgegan. undz veys mir nisht fun... un azoy iz es geven!

154
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:16,630
me hot im nebekh geharget un geshlogn. s'iz geven zeyer shlekht.

155
00:10:16,851 --> 00:10:18,069
zeyer shlekht.

156
00:10:18,413 --> 00:10:21,389
vu zenen arayngekumen, iz gevorn nokh arger

157
00:10:21,496 --> 00:10:27,969
vi in Ungarn far in in f- in re- REGULAR Ungarn. nokh arger geven.

158
00:10:28,540 --> 00:10:30,238
ven hot dos ongehoybn?

159
00:10:30,238 --> 00:10:31,989
azoy gikh vi zey zenen arayngekumen?

160
00:10:31,832 --> 00:10:34,017
azoy vi gikh zenen arayn, s-

161
00:10:34,144 --> 00:10:37,097
zey hobn zikh shoyn gebitn, di OFFICES,

162
00:10:37,353 --> 00:10:39,631
zenen araynkumen ales antisemitn,

163
00:10:39,758 --> 00:10:41,775
di zhandarn shlekhte,

164
00:10:41,898 --> 00:10:43,838
dos iz, ales iz geven shoyn

165
00:10:43,961 --> 00:10:46,917
ungarishe. biter. farbitert.

166
00:10:47,266 --> 00:10:49,505
zey hobn dokh gevust shoyn vos Hitler vil.

167
00:10:49,872 --> 00:10:53,522
SO, hob zey shoyn ales geton vos zey hobn gevolt.

168
00:10:53,987 --> 00:10:58,855
vos fara gezetsn, akhuts dos men ken nit shlofn bay emetsn,

169
00:10:58,855 --> 00:11:00,259
vos fara andere gezetsn...

170
00:11:00,223 --> 00:11:04,859
me hot nisht getort redn in der gas, dray mentshn hobn nisht getort zayn in tsuzamen.

171
00:11:07,609 --> 00:11:12,685
dray mentshn hobn nisht ge-, ikh bin geforn, ikh hob gedarft aroyfforn keyn Siget,

172
00:11:12,858 --> 00:11:17,374
s'iz geven a BUS, a groyser BUS, vos zey flegn nemen di mentshn tsu forn keyn Siget,

173
00:11:19,075 --> 00:11:23,794
un s'iz geven mayne a COUSIN fun tatn's tsad fun an andere de- de- k- s-,

174
00:11:26,173 --> 00:11:28,676
er hot ober genekhtikt bayn undz.

175
00:11:29,881 --> 00:11:33,397
un er hot zikh gebetn, vayl er hot nisht gehat vu tsu shlofn ober,

176
00:11:33,443 --> 00:11:37,621
mir hobn im ongezogt, zolstu visn du kenst nisht zogn az du host do geshlofn.

177
00:11:38,064 --> 00:11:42,710
m- un er iz geshtanen un er hot geredt mit mir, iz er oykh aroyfgeforn mitn BUS,

178
00:11:42,997 --> 00:11:45,451
hot men im arayngerufn, hot men gefregt,

179
