un dey, dey ungarishe mentshn hobn nisht ge-

395
00:22:47,372 --> 00:22:48,914
g- d-...

396
00:22:48,914 --> 00:22:49,934
di...

397
00:22:49,954 --> 00:22:55,725
di eydele mentshn, di doktoyrim mit di LAWYERS, mit azoyne zakhn, zey zenen nisht geven gevoynt mit

398
00:22:55,782 --> 00:22:58,790
droysn arbet. zey zenen nebekh oysgeshtorbn.

399
00:22:58,804 --> 00:23:01,798
oysgeshtorbn, zeyer UNK.

400
00:22:59,415 --> 00:23:01,507
un vu hot men geshikt ayer man?

401
00:23:01,812 --> 00:23:06,453
hot men, iz azoy geven. hot er mir geshribn a kartl,

402
00:23:06,753 --> 00:23:10,429
az ikh zol im brengen, me hot dort tsugelozt

403
00:23:10,539 --> 00:23:17,196
az me zol zey epes brengen. ikh zol dem brengen dos vinter zakhn.

404
00:23:17,315 --> 00:23:24,773
un ikh zol im brengen epes tsu esn. hob ikh gekoyft gereykherte gendzene CHI- fleysh.

405
00:23:24,889 --> 00:23:30,138
un, farshidene zakhn vos ikh hob farshtanen se ken shteyn a bisl.

406
00:23:30,245 --> 00:23:34,182
un ikh hob im gekoyft varemdike zakhn ontsutun.

407
00:23:35,199 --> 00:23:37,532
un ikh bin ongekumen ahin,

408
00:23:38,566 --> 00:23:39,887
un,

409
00:23:40,063 --> 00:23:43,124
s'iz geven an oylem vos zol ikh aykh zogn,

410
00:23:43,231 --> 00:23:45,501
az himl hobn zikh nisht geefnt,

411
00:23:45,501 --> 00:23:48,000
vet es keyn mol nisht...

412
00:23:48,841 --> 00:23:51,034
ikh hob im koym gefinen.

413
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,925
un ven ikh hob im gefinen tut er a zog,

414
00:23:54,096 --> 00:23:58,277
"yo, me shikt mikh aroys keyn Ukrayne." zog ikh, "NO, dikh vet men nisht aroysshikn."

415
00:23:59,729 --> 00:24:04,618
s'hot, ikh hob epes a zog gegebn, ikh hob aroysgezogt dos vort, "NO, me vet dikh nisht shikn."

416
00:24:05,710 --> 00:24:08,529
un s'iz ongenumen gevorn, mayn vort.

417
00:24:08,635 --> 00:24:14,197
"yo," zogt er, "ikh bin shoyn ober ikh gey shoyn, ikh bin shoyn azoy..." zog ikh, "NO, me vet dikh nisht shikn."

418
00:24:14,622 --> 00:24:18,433
un s'iz geven a zuntik, un zuntik UNK bin ikh shoyn aheymgekumen,

419
00:24:20,046 --> 00:24:22,531
montik hob ikh gefast.

420
00:24:22,938 --> 00:24:24,772
ikh hob gevust er fort aroys,

421
00:24:24,907 --> 00:24:32,724
un ikh bin, ikh hob a COUSIN do, ot o, er hot gevoynt in Debretsin, un ikh bin tsugegangen tsun im, un ikh hob im gezogt, zog ikh, "zolstu visn Avrom Meyern

422
00:24:32,814 --> 00:24:34,768
shikt men aroys keyn Ukrayne."

423
00:24:36,669 --> 00:24:40,672
un, ikh kum a- ikh kum aheym shoyn, s'iz oyf der nakht,

424
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:47,550
un koydem nemt er mikh a bisl in shtot, un er zogt, "lomir hern vos se hert zikh, lomir d- durkhgeyn a bisl di shtot."

425
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:50,708
nu, se vert shpet, zogt er, "gey aheym du darfst oyffastn."

426
00:24:50,998 --> 00:24:52,407
ikh kum aheym,

427
00:24:52,517 --> 00:24:55,695
ale in in hoyf vu ho'mir gevoynt,

428
00:24:55,798 --> 00:24:59,340
"oy Dinele, Dinele, dayn man iz gekumen er zukht dikh."

429
00:24:59,792 --> 00:25:02,694
zog ikh, "mayn man iz gekumen er zukht mikh?"

430
00:25:02,957 --> 00:25:07,007
"yo, mir hobn im gezogt du bist in shtot, zikher iz er gegangen tsu dayn COUSIN."

431
00:25:07,121 --> 00:25:08,316
SO ikh hob shoyn

432
00:25:08,458 --> 00:25:12,841
nisht gevolt, ikh bin tsugegan nor tsu dem toyer, tsu zen tsi er kumt,

433
00:25:12,958 --> 00:25:18,318
un ikh bin geVOKT a bisl azoy, ikh hob im bagegnt, er iz tsurikgekumen, me hot im gezogt er iz take geven dortn.

434
00:25:18,435 --> 00:25:21,534
un me hot im, un er hot gehat a bruder oykh in Debretsin,

435
00:25:22,151 --> 00:25:25,178
un me hot im gezogt az ikh bin shoyn aheymgekumen.

436
00:25:25,899 --> 00:25:28,737
SO iz er aheymgekumen oyf urloyb,

437
00:25:28,885 --> 00:25:30,617
oyf tsen teg.

438
00:25:31,077 --> 00:25:33,930
zog ikh, "zestu, ikh hob gezogt me vet dikh nisht shikn."

439
00:25:34,028 --> 00:25:37,088
zogt er, "ober ikh darf dokh tsurikgeyn, me vet dokh mikh yo shikn."

440
00:25:37,186 --> 00:25:39,613
ven iz tsurikgegan, di tsen teg,

441
00:25:39,749 --> 00:25:42,846
hot men tsurikgenumen di ale yinglekh.

442
00:25:43,121 --> 00:25:46,860
in di raye. un me hot zey gefregt,

443
00:25:47,253 --> 00:25:50,324
"vos bistu?" eyner hot gezogt a dokter.

444
00:25:50,582 --> 00:25:54,030
"gey in der zayt." eyner hot gezogt a shuster, "gey in der zayt."

445
00:25:54,129 --> 00:25:59,101
eyner hot gezogt a, a LAWYER, "der zayt." der hot gezogt aza arbayter un der hot

446
00:25:59,220 --> 00:26:04,908
az me hot oysgekloybn, hot er gezen zey kloybn oys di arbayters, ir farshteyt?

447
00:26:05,009 --> 00:26:09,764
un deye ales. hot er gezogt dem emes. zogt er, "ikh bin a BADOGOS.

448
00:26:09,974 --> 00:26:13,830
dos heyst oyf ungarish a BADOGOS, a SHEET METAL, BADOGOS.

449
00:26:14,237 --> 00:26:15,882
hot men im geshtelt in der zayt.

450
00:26:16,408 --> 00:26:20,209
deye ale hot men nisht aroysgeshikt, un dey ale,

451
00:26:20,361 --> 00:26:26,855
dey LAWYERS, mit di doktoyrim, mit di shraybers, mit ale HET hot men aroysgeshikt take. un im UNK geblibn.

452
00:26:27,289 --> 00:26:30,046
un me ho'mir gearbet biz,

453
00:26:30,812 --> 00:26:34,936
ven in, detsember, ven ikh hob shoyn gehat dos kind

454
00:26:35,038 --> 00:26:37,213
er iz nisht geveb shoyn in der heym ober,

455
00:26:37,325 --> 00:26:43,244
er iz geven, ober er hot gearbet in in Debretsin. ikh fleg im trogn ayedn oyf der nakht esn afile.

456
00:26:44,642 --> 00:26:49,604
un nokh dem hot men im shoyn oykh aroysgeshikt shoyn in in,

457
00:26:50,061 --> 00:26:53,790
s'iz geven shoyn in yener un feber,

458
00:26:53,913 --> 00:26:55,013
ober

459
00:26:55,124 --> 00:26:59,931
zey zenen nokh alts geven in Ungarn, in land. ober nisht in Debretsin, vayter in

460
00:27:00,027 --> 00:27:03,614
Kleynvardan un azoy in far, ale shtet zenen zey az...

461
00:27:03,747 --> 00:27:07,113
nokher zenen zey oykhet aroysgeforn. ober er iz geven

462
00:27:07,283 --> 00:27:09,729
azoy gevoynt mit di keltn.

463
00:27:09,866 --> 00:27:12,689
er iz geven gevoynt mit di ale zakhn.

464
00:27:12,873 --> 00:27:20,187
nisht azoy vi di eydele mentshn, di doktoyrim mit deye zakhn. er hot durkhgebrokhn, un er hot zeyer shver gearbet dortn.

465
00:27:20,327 --> 00:27:23,466
er hot zeyer shver gearbet. er iz ongekumen keyn Ukrayne,

466
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:25,724
hot men im, getsaygt di goyim,

467
00:27:25,843 --> 00:27:30,959
a barg, vu di barg zogn zey hot zikh nayn tog gehoybn

468
00:27:31,063 --> 00:27:33,637
vu me hot geshosn di mentshn un

469
00:27:33,949 --> 00:27:36,937
fun eyn shos vert men nokh nisht toyt!

470
00:27:37,047 --> 00:27:41,547
nor me hot zikh tsugedekt hot zikh di barg gehoybn, nayn teg hot zikh di barg gehoybn.

471
00:27:41,913 --> 00:27:46,084
SO er iz geven oyf zeyer shlekhte PLACES. er iz geven der ershter,

472
00:27:46,174 --> 00:27:49,634
in in mit zayne kleyder, un mit zayne zakhn

473
00:27:49,746 --> 00:27:52,684
tsu trogn di munitsye tsu, tsum front.

474
00:27:53,219 --> 00:27:56,596
di gantse tsayt hot ir gevust vi, vu er iz?

475
00:27:56,142 --> 00:27:56,605
NO.

476
00:27:56,596 --> 00:27:57,766
ir hot nisht gevust?

477
00:27:57,132 --> 00:27:57,884
NO.

478
00:27:57,766 --> 00:28:00,860
ven ir hot gehat dos kind er iz, iz er shoyn nisht geven.

479
00:28:00,953 --> 00:28:05,103
ikh hob gehat dos kind, un dernokh hob ikh im geshikt a telegram,

480
00:28:05,634 --> 00:28:08,278
hot men im koydem nisht gelozt avekshikn.

481
00:28:08,381 --> 00:28:09,595
aheymkumen.

482
00:28:09,706 --> 00:28:14,486
den, hot men im geshikt nokh a telegram, funem HOSPITAL,

483
00:28:14,610 --> 00:28:17,446
demolts hot men im gelozt aheym oyf a tsvey teg.

484
00:28:17,911 --> 00:28:24,908
un demolts hob ikh im nokh gezen, un dernokh iz er tsurikgeforn, un nisht mer, er iz oykh aroysgeforn keyn Ukrayne.

485
00:28:25,227 --> 00:28:32,604
un, ven ir hot gehat dos kind hot ir gekent geyn in in zayn in vos- vosere shpitol ir vilt?

486
00:28:32,024 --> 00:28:33,111
NO.

487
00:28:33,250 --> 00:28:37,216
NO, s'iz nisht geven erge-, nor eyn shpitol.

488
00:28:37,118 --> 00:28:40,212
 eyn shpitol, ober far yidn, yidn hobn dortn...

489
00:28:39,967 --> 00:28:44,304
yidn un goyim. yidn un goyim. ober zenen shoyn geven zeyer antisemitn.

490
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,264
un vi azoy hot zikh dos bavizn?

491
00:28:46,195 --> 00:28:47,289
 bay z-...

492
00:28:47,959 --> 00:28:53,512
veyst dokh, an ershtling iz dokh nisht gring tsu hobn. hob ikh gekrekhtst.

493
00:28:54,091 --> 00:28:58,103
makht a NURSE, zi iz geven azoy a MIDvayb,

494
00:28:58,244 --> 00:29:00,114
nisht a REGULAR NURSE,

495
00:29:00,284 --> 00:29:03,560
zogt zi, "nor di tsigayner un di yidn krekhtsn."

496
00:29:04,087 --> 00:29:08,470
zi hot aroysgegebn, ir farshteyt, di verter tsu zogn,

497
00:29:08,942 --> 00:29:13,514
kent aykh forshteln vi azoy ikh hob gelitn, ven ikh hob gehert di zakhn.

498
00:29:13,663 --> 00:29:20,407
az s'iz nor di yidn mit di tsigayner. zey hobn aroysgevizn, zey hobn shtark aroysgevizn di antisemitkeyt, yo.

499
00:29:20,751 --> 00:29:23,788
iz geven meglekh, um,

500
00:29:23,788 --> 00:29:25,825
tsu hobn a bris?

501
00:29:26,579 --> 00:29:29,779
yo, in der heym, in der heym, yo.

502
00:29:31,985 --> 00:29:37,419
 vos iz geven fun nayntsn tsvey un fertsik on, vi azoy hot ir gelebt?

503
00:29:38,163 --> 00:29:40,079
ikh hob gearbet.

504
00:29:40,211 --> 00:29:41,928
un ver hot akhtung gegebn oyf

505
00:29:41,928 --> 00:29:44,588
 dos kind iz geboyrn gevorn in dray un fertsik.

506
00:29:43,291 --> 00:29:44,633
in dray un fertsik.

507
00:29:44,588 --> 00:29:47,569
nokh dem, ober nokh dos kind.

508
00:29:44,633 --> 00:29:46,291
biz demolts hob ikh gearbet,

